"Iha is on Instagram! I thought it was a April fish!" wrote an X user in reaction to the launch. Some users joked that it was good that the reals had chosen the most 'civilized' Instagram instead of X, ex Twitter. Naruhito rose to the throne of the Chrysanthemum in 2019 in a traditional ceremony after his father, very popular, became the first emperor to abdicate in over two centuries.
Other monarchies have created social media accounts, including British royals, which have recently been at the centre of a storm of complottist voices and theories. The manipulation of a family photo released from the palace to the media has fueled online speculations on the fate of Kate Middleton, Princess of Wales, who after days of mystery revealed to be sick of cancer.&nbsp;
